A high-fidelity macro studio product visualization cross-section cutaway of a modular flight suit torso armor panel. The outermost 1.5mm active chameleon stealth skin consists of a flexible transparent polyurethanic hydrogel layer patterned with micro-etched vertical channel rows holding suspended 130nm guanine nanocrystals. The structural core shows a thick, matte-black 12.0mm aerospace-grade carbon fiber polycarbonate weave showing embedded continuous graphene ground lines. The innermost layer features a removable 18.0mm teal-colored variable-density flexible elastomer rib liner displaying hollow pneumatic breathing loops and micro-capillary paths, realistic studio overhead cross-lighting, photorealistic material and resin textures, 8k --ar 16:9
